dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for Buffalo County, Wisconsin in YE2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Buffalo_Addresses_YE2016.gdb.[Site address points represent the location of site or service delivery addresses assigned by local governments.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://www.buffalocountywi.gov/185/GIS-Land-Information-Office. This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
